<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>ج ز أ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[١١٦٥ - ج ز أ]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>جزَأَ/ جزَأَ بـ يَجزَأ، جَزْءًا، فهو جازِئ، والمفعول مَجْزوء<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">• جزَأ الرغيفَ:</span> قسّمه أجزاء.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">• جزَأ بالشَّيء:</span> اكتفى به وقنع.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>